LAZYVIM CHEATSHEET

USAGE: nvim [file] [options]
       Leader key: Space

GENERAL:
  :q                          Quit
  :w                          Save
  :wq or :x                   Save and quit
  <leader>qq                  Quit all
  <leader>fn                  New file
  <leader>l                   Lazy (plugin manager)
  <leader>L                   LazyVim changelog

NAVIGATION:
  h/j/k/l                     Left/down/up/right
  w/b                         Next/previous word
  0/$                         Start/end of line
  gg/G                        Start/end of file
  <C-u>/<C-d>                 Half page up/down
  <C-b>/<C-f>                 Full page up/down
  %                           Jump to matching bracket
  gd                          Go to definition
  gr                          Go to references
  K                           Hover documentation

EDITING:
  i/a                         Insert before/after cursor
  I/A                         Insert at start/end of line
  o/O                         New line below/above
  x/X                         Delete char forward/backward
  dd                          Delete line
  yy                          Yank (copy) line
  p/P                         Paste after/before cursor
  u/<C-r>                     Undo/redo
  .                           Repeat last command
  gcc                         Toggle comment line
  gc{motion}                  Toggle comment motion

WINDOW MANAGEMENT:
  <C-h/j/k/l>                 Navigate windows
  <leader>w                   Window picker
  <leader>-                   Split window below
  <leader>|                   Split window right
  <leader>wd                  Delete window
  <C-Up/Down>                 Resize window
  <leader>wm                  Maximize toggle

BUFFER MANAGEMENT:
  <S-h>/<S-l>                 Previous/next buffer
  <leader>bd                  Delete buffer
  <leader>bD                  Delete buffer (force)
  <leader>bb                  Switch to other buffer
  <leader>`                   Switch to last buffer
  <leader>,                   Switch buffer (telescope)

FILE EXPLORER (Neo-tree):
  <leader>e                   Toggle file explorer
  <leader>E                   Explorer current file location
  a                           Add file/directory
  d                           Delete
  r                           Rename
  y                           Copy
  x                           Cut
  p                           Paste
  <CR>                        Open
  s                           Open split
  S                           Open vsplit

SEARCH & FIND (Telescope):
  <leader><space>             Find files
  <leader>ff                  Find files
  <leader>fr                  Recent files
  <leader>fb                  Buffers
  <leader>fg                  Live grep
  <leader>fh                  Help pages
  <leader>fk                  Keymaps
  <leader>fc                  Find config files
  <leader>fs                  Select colorscheme
  <leader>/                   Grep current buffer
  <leader>sw                  Search word under cursor
  <leader>sW                  Search WORD under cursor

LSP FEATURES:
  gd                          Go to definition
  gr                          Go to references
  gI                          Go to implementation
  gy                          Go to type definition
  K                           Hover
  gK                          Signature help
  <leader>ca                  Code action
  <leader>rn                  Rename
  <leader>cf                  Format
  ]d/[d                       Next/prev diagnostic
  <leader>cd                  Line diagnostics
  <leader>cl                  Lsp info

GIT INTEGRATION:
  <leader>gg                  Lazygit
  <leader>gb                  Git blame line
  ]h/[h                       Next/prev hunk
  <leader>ghp                 Preview hunk
  <leader>ghr                 Reset hunk
  <leader>ghs                 Stage hunk
  <leader>ghS                 Stage buffer
  <leader>ghu                 Undo stage hunk
  <leader>ghR                 Reset buffer

TERMINAL:
  <leader>ft                  Terminal (root dir)
  <leader>fT                  Terminal (cwd)
  <C-/>                       Toggle terminal
  <C-_>                       which_key help
  <Esc><Esc>                  Enter normal mode (in terminal)

CODING HELPERS:
  <leader>cm                  Mason (LSP installer)
  <leader>cs                  Symbols outline
  <leader>xq                  Quickfix list
  <leader>xl                  Location list
  <leader>xt                  Todo comments
  <leader>xT                  Todo/Fix/Fixme
  <leader>st                  Search todos

UI TOGGLES:
  <leader>uf                  Toggle format on save
  <leader>us                  Toggle spelling
  <leader>uw                  Toggle word wrap
  <leader>ul                  Toggle line numbers
  <leader>ud                  Toggle diagnostics
  <leader>uc                  Toggle conceal
  <leader>uh                  Toggle highlight search
  <leader>ui                  Toggle indent guides

PLUGIN MANAGEMENT:
  <leader>l                   Open Lazy
  <leader>lu                  Lazy update
  <leader>ls                  Lazy sync
  <leader>lp                  Lazy profile
  <leader>li                  Lazy info
